==Sanskrit==

===Adjective===
'''dhṛta'''

# [[held]], borne, maintained, supported kept, possessed; used, practised, observed; measured, weighed; worn (as clothes, shoes, beard,) kept back, detained, by the hand) drawn tight (reins) turned towards or fixed upon, ready or prepared for, resolved on (loc. or dat.) continuing, existing, being; prolonged (in pronunciation) solemnly, slowly.